                  , <rs id="t17650227-43-viclabel270" type="occupation">Bart.</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17650227-43-victim502 t17650227-43-viclabel270"></join> did break and enter, and stealing a woollen cloth coat, value 30 s. and two guineas and a half, the property of the said Sir Alexander and a woollen cloth coat, value 18 s. and a pair of shoes, value 2 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17650227-43-person503">
